.SH NAME
\f[CR]ntp\-ctl\f[R] \- management client for the ntpd\-rs ntp\-daemon
process
.SH SYNOPSIS
\f[CR]ntp\-ctl\f[R] validate [\f[CR]\-c\f[R] \f[I]path\f[R]]
.PD 0
.P
.PD
\f[CR]ntp\-ctl\f[R] status [\f[CR]\-f\f[R] \f[I]format\f[R]]
